data.description: Custom-built stone Cape Cod, a hidden gem nestled on 100 acres of breathtaking landscape. Embrace the allure of nature with 45 tillable acres, 50 wooded acres, and meticulously manicured 5 acres. The property boasts a three-car garage, featuring a spacious apartment above—an ideal hunting lodge for those seeking a true hunter's paradise. Seize this one-of-a-kind opportunity to own a slice of tranquility and sophistication. Don't miss out on the chance to call this unique property your own.
